ftalb0gjs0j30mf02o0jr.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p> <ol><li>输入如下命令行</li></ol> <div class=\"language-json extra-class\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code>mongod --dbpath d<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>\\mongo\\data --journal\n</code></pre></div><p>看到 waiting for connections on port 27017 等，说明启动成功\n在浏览器输入</p> <div class=\"language-json extra-class\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code>localhost<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">27017</span>\n</code></pre></div><p><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0060lm7Tly1ftalgd7kcfj30nf0db3ye.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p> <p>看到此图，说明启动成功</p> <p>5.再次找到cmd.exe,再次进入到mongoDB的bin目录（因为，我没有配置环境变量，所以需要进到bin下面执行），输入mongo回车\n<img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0060lm7Tly1ftaljlflmjj30my0qfaae.jpg\" alt=\"image\"></p> <p>说明启动成功啦</p> "),_vm._ssrNode("<p>","</p>",[_vm._ssrNode("参考:\n"),_vm._ssrNode("<a href=\"http://www.imooc.com/article/18438\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">","</a>",[_vm._ssrNode("windows32位系统 安装MongoDB"),_c('OutboundLink')],2)],2)],2)}
